-- JBS’s Vigor Unit to Triple Sales in 5-10 Years, Valor Reports
-- B y   L u c i a   K a s s a i
-- 2012-02-13T11:44:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-13/jbs-s-vigor-unit-to-triple-sales-in-5-10-years-valor-reports.html
JBS SA (JBSS3) ’s Vigor Alimentos SA dairy
unit plans to more than triple sales in five to 10 years, Valor
Economico reported, citing Chief Executive Officer Gilberto
Xando.  JBS CEO Wesley Batista said Dec. 19 he was targeting sales
of 5 billion reais ($2.9 billion) at the unit by 2015, up from
1.5 billion reais last year.  To contact the reporter on this story:
